p: The essential oils CIV17-EO and NAV19-EO did not possess any antioxidant capacity, while CdG19-EO showed weak activity. The latter EO consists mainly of methyleugenol (41.5%), 1,8 cineole (39.7%) and limonene (7.6%), a composition which could explain the higher antioxidant activity compared to the other [ 20, 21].
